Summary: series of sightings, Duanesburg NY, in June-July '07 POSSIBLE UBDUCTION
divs: Sighting DetailsI have seen quite a few (more than usual) speedy little discs zipping around. They are too fast to be planes or satillites. No con trails. Very shiny, and they also change direction fast, and sometimes just vanish. Also, a few months before, I awoke with a start at about 10:30 PM, sweating like crazy. I felt more frightened than ever in my life. I am 100% sure didn't I didn't have a dream, but i feel that something bad happened to me or my mind... DO NOT E-MAIL ME, I DO NOT WISH TO BE INTERVIEWED.
